# VITE_FORMSPREE_ID: Formspree form ID for the RSVP + Wishes forms.
# Create one free form at https://formspree.io, then copy the ID from your
# endpoint URL (https://formspree.io/f/XXXXXXXX  ->  the XXXXXXXX part).
# Both forms post to this single endpoint; submissions are tagged with a
# hidden `type` field ("RSVP" or "Wish") so you can tell them apart.
# In Vercel: Project Settings -> Environment Variables -> add VITE_FORMSPREE_ID.
VITE_FORMSPREE_ID="your_formspree_id"
